<br>
Yibo<br>
54th Wanderer<br>
The Seventh Hammer <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udebaser2000.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Debaser2000</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/9/01 1:38:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> I'm not sure when you need gnome faction for the epic, unless for the gnome in the Overthere for the Cleansed Spirit of Kunark?<br>
<br>
But if you want to raise your gnome faction, kill minotaurs in Steamfont.  If you're camping the Hero, just clear out the caves between PH pops.  The gnomes will love you in no time.  Although I'm not sure they should after you slaughtered so many of their people.  :)<br>
<br>
Debaser Unsung<br>
56th Druid of Karana<br>
Champions in Arms<br>
Quellious Server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyibo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yibo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/10/01 6:52:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> I mended my evil ways.  I promise.  I had a tumultuous youth.<br>
<br>
Yibo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyibo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yibo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/10/01 11:04:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> You have to turn in the Gleaming Unicorn Horn to Silox Azrix in Akanon.  Is he far enough away from any guards/NPC's that faction is unimportant? <p>--Yibo<BR>
--53rd Wanderer of the Revelation<BR>
--The Seventh Hammer</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukorwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Korwin</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_yellowspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/10/01 1:29:08 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://lordfate.homestead.com/files/misc/KorAysa3.jpg height=162 width=109></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> He stands next to a greenie gnome right across from the mines of malfunction.  As far as I could see there weren't any other npcs close.<br>
<br>
As long as you're not KoS to him you should have no problem turning your horn in. <p><IMG SRC="http://lordfate.homestead.com/files/misc/sig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueiladwen123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eiladwen123</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/10/01 8:14:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> As far as I can remember Silox is not on any faction. There is a greeny gnome beside him that would probably be KoS to you but im pretty sure that Silox will be indifferent as gnomes are dubious to me and he conned indifferent. Try invising and running over to him. Should work :) <p>Eiladwen Treebarker
55th Preserver of Tunare
Lightbringers</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uboogahzdokupuppy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Boogahz Dokupuppy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/10/01 11:13:56 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> The quest Gnome was Amiable to me, but Sanfyrd (the Gnome behind him was scowling and green as all heck).  I had a chanter with me just in case, but I just crawled out of the water by the Gnome I needed and had no problem at all. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyibo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yibo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/11/01 9:37:34 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Question - Epic</span><hr size=1> excellent.  thanks everyone!<br>
